{"text_id":49513,"tokens":["**","The"," Benefits"," of"," Seeking"," Advice"," from"," Multiple"," People"," When"," Making"," a"," Decision","**","\n\n","Decision","-","making"," is"," an"," integral"," part"," of"," both"," personal"," and"," professional"," life","."," From"," choosing"," a"," career"," path"," to"," making"," business"," investments",","," the"," choices"," we"," make"," have"," far","-","reaching"," consequences","."," One"," effective"," strategy"," for"," making"," informed"," decisions"," is"," to"," seek"," advice"," from"," multiple"," individuals","."," This"," approach"," has"," several"," benefits",","," including"," a"," broader"," perspective",","," reduction"," of"," bias",","," and"," increased"," confidence"," in"," the"," decision",".","\n\n","**","1","."," Bro","ader"," Perspective","**","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," primary"," advantages"," of"," consulting"," multiple"," people"," is"," the"," acquisition"," of"," a"," broader"," perspective","."," Different"," individuals"," can"," offer"," unique"," insights"," based"," on"," their"," diverse"," experiences"," and"," expertise","."," For"," example",","," when"," a"," business"," owner"," is"," considering"," expanding"," into"," a"," new"," market",","," consulting"," various"," experts","\u2014","market"," analysts",","," industry"," veterans",","," and"," financial"," advisors","\u2014","can"," provide"," a"," well","-","rounded"," view"," of"," potential"," opportunities"," and"," risks","."," Each"," advisor"," may"," highlight"," different"," aspects",","," such"," as"," cultural"," nuances",","," economic"," indicators",","," or"," regulatory"," hurdles",","," thus"," enriching"," the"," decision","-","maker","'","s"," understanding"," and"," leading"," to"," a"," more"," comprehensive"," analysis"," of"," the"," situation",".","\n\n","**","2","."," Reduction"," of"," Bias","**","\n\n","Every"," individual"," has"," inherent"," biases"," that"," can"," cloud"," judgment","."," By"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources",","," decision","-","makers"," can"," mitigate"," the"," influence"," of"," these"," biases","."," Psychological"," research"," supports"," this"," notion",","," illustrating"," that"," group"," decisions"," often"," outperform"," individual"," decisions"," because"," diverse"," viewpoints"," can"," counter","balance"," confounding"," prejudices"," (","Su","row","iec","ki",","," ","2","0","0","4",")."," For"," instance",","," in"," a"," hiring"," process",","," considering"," feedback"," from"," multiple"," interviewers"," can"," help"," overcome"," the"," biases"," of"," any"," single"," interviewer",","," such"," as"," favor","itism"," or"," affinity"," bias",","," leading"," to"," a"," more"," objective"," assessment"," of"," the"," candidates",".","\n\n","**","3","."," Increased"," Confidence"," and"," Validation","**","\n\n","Consulting"," multiple"," advisors"," also"," helps"," in"," validating"," the"," final"," decision","."," When"," several"," knowledgeable"," people"," converge"," on"," similar"," advice",","," it"," adds"," credibility"," to"," the"," chosen"," path","."," This"," validation"," can"," boost"," confidence"," in"," the"," decision","-","maker",","," reducing"," the"," anxiety"," often"," associated"," with"," significant"," choices","."," For"," instance",","," a"," student"," deciding"," on"," a"," university"," program"," might"," seek"," advice"," from"," current"," students",","," alumni",","," and"," academic"," counselors","."," If"," these"," advisors"," consistently"," recommend"," the"," same"," program"," based"," on"," its"," curriculum",","," reputation",","," and"," career"," prospects",","," the"," student"," is"," likely"," to"," feel"," more"," confident"," in"," making"," that"," decision",".","\n\n","**","4","."," Identification"," of"," Blind"," Spots","**","\n\n","People"," are"," often"," unaware"," of"," their"," blind"," spots","\u2014","areas"," they"," overlook"," due"," to"," lack"," of"," knowledge"," or"," awareness","."," Multiple"," advisors"," can"," help"," identify"," these"," blind"," spots",","," preventing"," costly"," mistakes","."," In"," project"," management",","," for"," example",","," consulting"," team"," members"," from"," different"," departments"," (","e",".","g",".,"," engineering",","," marketing",","," finance",")"," can"," unearth"," potential"," challenges"," that"," may"," not"," have"," been"," apparent"," from"," a"," single"," perspective","."," This"," collaborative"," approach"," can"," lead"," to"," more"," robust"," planning"," and"," execution",".","\n\n","**","5","."," Enhancing"," Creativity","**","\n\n","Diverse"," opinions"," can"," spark"," innovative"," solutions","."," When"," faced"," with"," a"," problem",","," hearing"," various"," viewpoints"," can"," lead"," to"," the"," synthesis"," of"," ideas"," that"," wouldn","'","t"," have"," emerged"," in"," isolation","."," For"," example",","," in"," product"," development",","," brainstorming"," sessions"," with"," a"," cross","-","functional"," team"," can"," lead"," to"," creative"," breakthroughs"," that"," a"," homogeneous"," group"," might"," not"," achieve","."," Research"," in"," organizational"," behavior"," highlights"," that"," diversity"," in"," teams"," enhances"," creative"," performance"," and"," problem","-","solving"," (","Page",","," ","2","0","0","7",").","\n\n","**","Conclusion","**","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," when"," making"," decisions"," offers"," numerous"," benefits",","," including"," a"," broader"," perspective",","," reduced"," bias",","," increased"," confidence",","," identification"," of"," blind"," spots",","," and"," enhanced"," creativity","."," By"," leveraging"," the"," collective"," knowledge"," and"," experience"," of"," a"," diverse"," group",","," decision","-","makers"," can"," make"," more"," informed",","," objective",","," and"," innovative"," choices","."," Therefore",","," whether"," faced"," with"," personal"," challenges"," or"," professional"," dilemmas",","," it"," is"," prudent"," to"," cast"," a"," wide"," net"," for"," advice"," to"," navigate"," the"," complexities"," of"," decision","-","making"," successfully",".","\n\n","**","References",":**","\n\n","Page",","," S","."," E","."," (","2","0","0","7",")."," *","The"," Difference",":"," How"," the"," Power"," of"," Diversity"," Creates"," Better"," Groups",","," Firms",","," Schools",","," and"," Societies","*."," Princeton"," University"," Press",".","\n\n","Su","row","iec","ki",","," J","."," (","2","0","0","4",")."," *","The"," Wisdom"," of"," Crow","ds",":"," Why"," the"," Many"," Are"," Smarter"," Than"," the"," Few"," and"," How"," Collective"," Wisdom"," Shapes"," Business",","," Economies",","," Societies",","," and"," Nations","*."," Anchor"," Books","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"gpt4o","label":1}